import React from 'react'
import { Nav, 
         NavbarContainer, 
         MobileIcon, 
         NavLogo, 
         NavMenu, 
         NavItem, 
         NavLinks,
         NavItemBtn,
         NavBtnLink,
         Title,
         UserLink
         } from './Navbar.elements'
import {Button} from '../../../GlobalStyles'         
import {AiOutlineLogout} from 'react-icons/ai'
import {HiOutlineUser} from 'react-icons/hi'
import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {

  const [click, setClick] = useState(false)
  const [button, setButton] = useState(true)

  return (
    <>
      <Nav>
          <Title style={{color:'#200752'}}>Bonjour Mohamed !</Title>
          <NavMenu>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to ='profile'><HiOutlineUser style={{width:'2rem', height:'2rem'}}/></NavLinks>
              <UserLink to ='profile' >Mohamed Ziani</UserLink>
            </NavItem>
            <NavItem>
              <NavLinks to ='/'><AiOutlineLogout style={{width:'2rem', height:'2rem'}}/></NavLinks>
            </NavItem>
          </NavMenu>
      </Nav>
    </>
  )
}

export default Navbar
